snippet.title: Sword of Kadash Commodore 64
snippet.description:
A really great adventure RPG kind of but really fun an amazing game for its day.
And still fun. I checked you tube and found no videos on this game so I uploaded this so you can check out a sample of, "Sword of Kadash". I lost the beginning of this video so I trimmed off an error from the very beginning if I get a response I will try to load of few more of this one.
